value.title: Special Q&A Session with Pastor Tara
value.description: In this Special Question & Answer Session, Pastor Tara Akinkuade provides insightful answers to pressing questions that arise from various professional and academic pursuits. Drawing from the wisdom of God's word, she illuminates challenging topics and offers clarity to complex issues, helping attendees navigate their spiritual and practical lives. This session encourages listeners to engage with the teachings, share their experiences, and invite others to join the conversation on the Telegram channel, fostering a community of learning and transformation. Be inspired and uplifted as you explore the intersection of faith and everyday challenges.

value.title: Special Q&A Session with Pastor Tara
value.description: In this enlightening Special Question & Answer Session held in June 2025, Pastor Tara Akinkuade addresses various pressing questions that arise from different professional and academic spheres. Drawing from biblical teachings, she provides insightful answers that illuminate the complexities of life and work, encouraging listeners to seek understanding through God's word. This session emphasizes the transformative power of scripture, inviting participants to share their experiences and join a community of learners on a dedicated Telegram channel. Engage with these discussions to deepen your knowledge and faith, and invite others to partake in this spiritual journey.
